metadata.name: R00T
metadata.description:
I've been insecure about my teeth for as long as I can remember. Had countless dreams about them falling out.

They're out here causing me physical pain now, so they gotta go. 

Funny to think there's going to be a representation of that insecurity on the blockchain for eternity.

That internal insecurity isn't likely to go away anytime soon, but there's some catharsis in having vented to a decentralized network.
